  "body": "For some reason Pivot changes very often with very small jumps during the Ranges phase.\r\nIn the beginning the jumps are ok (should be bigger but are acceptable) but later during the Ranges phase the jumps are very often and usually just by one block.\r\nIt doesn't break anything but probably slows down the Ranges phase and maybe healing (more holes).\r\nIt only happens on my slower VM and causes more than 200 pivot changes in Ranges phase.\r\nThe faster VM works ok - just around 5 pivot changes. \r\n\r\n`SNAP - to many empty responses - Pivot changed from 15479802 to 15479803`\r\n\r\n[mainnet.logs.txt](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/9538862/mainnet.logs.txt)\r\n",
