    "body": "This seems likely due to:\r\n- Lack of throttling on response byte which tend to cause a lot of timeouts. Fixed by https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/pull/4528 (not in develop)\r\n- Combined with this logic, which seems to mean, if you have a lot of consecutive failures (probably because of previous issue), pivot get reset. https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/blob/master/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/SnapSync/SnapSyncFeed.cs#L179\r\n- Probably also due to lack of throttling on creating request, which increase the number of request. I'll make a PR for this... it makes download faster in any case.",
